## 3. 養聲

廣東話：你最近唱K唱得多，記得要多啲暖水，保護把聲，等把聲快啲好返，等於養聲咁話。
English: You sang a lot at karaoke recently, remember to drink more warm water to protect your voice, let it recover quickly, that's how you maintain your voice.

## 4. 票尾

廣東話：張飛上面寫住「票尾請妥善保存」，所以我唔會掉咗佢，等陣間拎去換停車場優惠。
English: The ticket says "please keep the stub properly", so I won't throw it away, I'll use it later to get the parking discount.

## 5. hacker

廣東話：聽講有啲 hacker 會入侵人哋電腦偷啲重要資料，真係要小心啲。
English: I heard some hackers would hack into other people's computers to steal important information, we really need to be careful.

## 6. 石斛蘭

廣東話：我屋企後院種咗幾盆石斛蘭，佢哋會依附住啲樹生長，開出嚟嘅花好靚。
English: I planted a few pots of dendrobium orchids in my backyard, they grow attached to trees, the flowers are really beautiful.

## 7. 吊詭（矛盾、悖論）

廣東話：佢話自己唔鍾意錢，但係又成日買啲貴嘢，真係好吊詭。
English: He says he doesn't like money, but he always buys expensive things, it's really contradictory.

## 8. 吊詭（似非而是、荒謬）

廣東話：呢個故仔個結局簡直吊詭，完全估佢唔到。
English: The ending of this story is really paradoxical, I totally didn't see it coming.

## 9. 各為其主

廣東話：呢場官司入面，兩個律師各為其主，梗係幫自己嘅客仔講嘢啦。
English: In this lawsuit, the two lawyers each serve their own master, of course they'll speak for their own clients.

## 10. 軨蓋

廣東話：咦，你架車個軨蓋爛咗，搵日要去車房整返好佢。
English: Hey, the tire cap of your car is broken, you need to go to the garage to fix it one of these days.

## 11. 打哥夫

廣東話：聽日放假，我約咗阿邊個去高爾夫球場打哥夫，你有無興趣一齊？
English: Tomorrow is a holiday, I arranged to play golf with some friends, are you interested in joining?

## 12. 免揀

廣東話：呢間鋪啲水果全部都已經包裝好晒，唔可以逐個揀，係免揀㗎。
English: All the fruits in this shop are already packaged, you can't pick one by one, it's non-selectable.

## 13. 擺闊佬

廣東話：佢今次請客嗰陣勁點好多嘢食，根本食唔晒，擺闊佬啫。
English: When he treated us this time, he ordered a lot of food, we couldn't finish it all, he was just showing off.

## 14. 廣播劇

廣東話：我阿婆最鍾意聽收音機播放嘅廣播劇，每日食完晏晝飯就會扭大聲聽。
English: My grandma loves listening to radio dramas broadcast on the radio, she turns up the volume after lunch every day.

## 15. 錄影機

廣東話：我屋企仲有一部舊式錄影機，可以錄低電視節目慢慢睇。
English: I still have an old VCR at home, I can record TV programs and watch them later.

## 16. 吟詩吟唔甩

廣東話：證據確鑿，佢想呃人都唔得，吟詩吟唔甩呀！
English: The evidence is conclusive, he can't fool anyone, there's no way to deny it!

## 17. 佈道大會

廣東話：聽講聽日教會會搞一個大型佈道大会，邀請咗好多牧師嚟講經。
English: I heard the church is holding a large-scale evangelistic conference tomorrow, they've invited many pastors to preach.

## 18. 寫手（寫作嘅人）

廣東話：佢係一個專業寫手，寫咗好多本暢銷書。
English: He's a professional writer, he's written many bestselling books.

## 19. 寫手（代替他人寫作嘅人）

廣東話：聽講有啲明星會請寫手幫手寫訪問稿，等自己講嘢顯得更有深度。
English: I heard some celebrities hire ghostwriters to help write interview scripts, to make themselves sound more profound.

## 20. 代打

廣東話：我今晚唔得閒打機，你帮我代打幾關啦！
English: I'm busy tonight, can you play the game for me for a few levels!

## 21. 茶碗

廣東話：日本茶道用到嘅茶碗通常都好精緻，唔係普通飲茶嗰啲杯。
English: The tea bowls used in Japanese tea ceremony are usually very delicate, not like the regular cups we use for drinking tea.

## 22. 茶隔

廣東話：如果你想啲茶乾淨啲，最好用茶隔隔一隔茶葉先斟。
English: If you want cleaner tea, it's best to use a tea strainer to filter the tea leaves before pouring.

## 23. 只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈

廣東話：呢間公司啲老闆自己就周圍去旅行，但係員工請假就唔批，真係只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈呀！
English: The bosses of this company go traveling everywhere themselves, but they don't approve of employees taking leave, it's really a case of "the magistrates can set fires but the common people can't light lamps"!

## 24. 獨唱

廣東話：今晚演唱會有個環節係獨唱環節，會有一位歌手自己一個上台表演。
English: Tonight's concert has a solo performance segment, where one singer will perform on stage alone.

## 25. 快人快事

廣東話：佢做嘢一向快人快事，唔會拖泥帶水，我好欣賞佢呢點。
English: He always handles things quickly and decisively, he doesn't drag things out, I really admire that about him.

## 26. 四腳獸

廣東話：喂，聽講出面緊嗰間公廁有人撞正四腳獸呀！
English: Hey, I heard someone caught a couple doing it in the act in that public toilet outside!

## 27. 無米粥

廣東話：件事而家仲係煲緊無米粥，雙方都未傾掂具體條件，唔好咁快落決定住。
English: The matter is still in the preliminary discussion stage, both parties haven't settled on the specific conditions yet, don't decide too quickly.

## 28. 義會

廣東話：以前啲低下層人士想借錢周轉，通常會join義會，等大家可以互相幫忙。
English: In the past, people from lower classes who wanted to borrow money for emergencies would usually join a rotating savings association, so everyone could help each other.

